Coach Tip: Keep your core tight and maintain proper form
Focus on controlled movement and full range of motion
Keep your knees behind your toes and chest up
Step forward and lower until both knees are at 90 degrees
Maintain steady pace throughout the run
Keep your body in a straight line from head to heels
Lift your shoulders off the ground using your abs
Keep your back straight and lift with your legs
Rest and recover for the next week
